('82', 'Riding', '10 Man Ride', '["https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=MA4KYHrD0ljXcilWfuXy","https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=mGNeYgNq7wbEuUBh3v3f","https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=3MVmxxCPw7qZbiXPkUbw","https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=Sv9VxjkK3vZBVzrSGzbG","https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=A0b6YHplRGT7UG0oaq2U"]'::jsonb, 'To create the time it takes to get into the 1 Man Ride - we must get in the face Of the first ball carrier so they can’t get up and out Early. Once the ball is passed adjacent - we can press up to cause turnovers. | We will create turnovers in the second level by doubling with our attackmen and midfielders. | If a player carries over the midline while in a double we must stay on that double and not let them free their hands. Think of it in the same way we would be doubling at the end of the game to get the ball back. | To get into the 10 Man Ride - the goalie will bump up a succession of players to the field. | If all of the clearing players are in front of the midline - we have to get a midfielder back before the pole can go over. When this happens we will have to alternate which side of the field has a midfielder back in order to press up to the defenseman.', '["<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=MA4KYHrD0ljXcilWfuXy\" style=\"max-width: 100%\"></iframe>","<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=mGNeYgNq7wbEuUBh3v3f\" style=\"max-width: 100%\"></iframe>","<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=3MVmxxCPw7qZbiXPkUbw\" style=\"max-width: 100%\"></iframe>","<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=Sv9VxjkK3vZBVzrSGzbG\" style=\"max-width: 100%\"></iframe>","<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://lacrosse.labradorsports.com/play?l=A0b6YHplRGT7UG0oaq2U\" style=\"max-width: 100%\"></iframe>"]'::jsonb, '09-14', '13-14', '13-14', TRUE, 'coaches', 'coaches_corner', 'https://powlax.com/mp-files/10-man-ride-pdf-lacrosse-powlax.pdf/', 1092018578, 'https://vimeo.com/1092018578', '[mpdl-file-link file_id=1257]', '["https://powlax.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/10-Man-Ride-Lacrosse-POWLAX.webp"]'::jsonb, '2025-08-05T04:08:10.823Z', '2025-08-05T04:08:10.823Z');
